William Beaudine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Beaudine 0 William Washington Beaudine (January 15, 1892 – March 18, 1970) was an American film actor and director. He was one of Hollywood's most prolific directors, turning out films in remarkable numbers and in a wide variety of genres.
